      <div type="page" n="137">
        <pb n="137"/>
        <lg xml:id="block_A" xml:lang="he" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2Fa8b1b4d4-80be-4f1b-b71b-ac258c3266fd.jp2/3052,532,1383,1806/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>קוֹל יְיָ חֹצֵב לַהֲבוֹת אֵשׁ,</l>
          <l>קוֹל יְיָ יָחִיל מִדְבָּר,</l>
          <l>יְיָ מִדְבַּר קָדֵשׁ.</l>
          <l>יָחִיל</l>
          <l>קוֹל יְיָ יְחוֹלֵל אַיָּלוֹת</l>
          <l>וַיִּחֲשֹׁף יְעָרוֹת</l>
          <l>וּבְהֵיכָלוֹ כֻּלּוֹ אֹמֵר כָּבוֹד.</l>
          <l>יְיָ לַמַּבּוּל יָשָׁב</l>
          <l>וַיֵּשֶׁב יְיָ מֶלֶךְ לְעוֹלָם.</l>
          <l>T</l>
          <l>י עז לְעַמּוֹ יִתֵּן,</l>
          <l>&gt;&gt;</l>
          <l>יְיָ יְבָרֵךְ אֶת־עַמּוֹ בַשָּׁלוֹם.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_B" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2Fa8b1b4d4-80be-4f1b-b71b-ac258c3266fd.jp2/997,503,1308,1841/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>Kol Adonai chotzeiv lahavot eish,</l>
          <l>kol Adonai yachil midbar,</l>
          <l>yachil Adonai midbar Kadeish.</l>
          <l>Kol Adonai y&apos;choleil ayalot</l>
          <l>vayechesof y&apos;arot</l>
          <l>uv&apos;heichalo kulo omeir kavod.</l>
          <l>Adonai lamabul yashav</l>
          <l>vayeishev Adonai Melech l&apos;olam.</l>
          <l>Adonai oz l&apos;amo yitein</l>
          <l>Adonai y&apos;vareich et amo vashalom.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_C" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2Fa8b1b4d4-80be-4f1b-b71b-ac258c3266fd.jp2/1553,2564,2211,1505/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>THE VOICE OF ADONAI kindles flames of fire;</l>
          <l>the voice of Adonai convulses the wilderness;</l>
          <l>Adonai convulses the wilderness of Kadesh;</l>
          <l>the voice of Adonai causes hinds to calve,</l>
          <l>and strips forests bare;</l>
          <l>while in God&apos;s temple all say &quot;Glory!&quot;</l>
          <l>Adonai sat enthroned at the Flood;</l>
          <l>Adonai sits enthroned, sovereign forever.</l>
          <l>May Adonai grant strength to God&apos;s people;</l>
          <l>may Adonai bestow on God&apos;s people wellbeing.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
